  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDataParser
    Base class for all SWE Common data stream parsers (text, binary, xml, json)
    AbstractDataWriter
    Base class for all SWE Common data stream writers (text, binary, xml, json)
    DataBlockProcessor
    Base class for all data block level processors.
    The processor tree is pre-configured so that the processing can occur very fast on many data blocks matching the same components structure.
    DataBlockProcessor.ArrayProcessor  
    DataBlockProcessor.BaseProcessor

    JsonDataParserGson
    New implementation of JSON data parser with better efficiency since the read tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
    JsonDataWriter
    New implementation of JSON data writer with better efficiency since the write tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
    JsonDataWriterGson
    New implementation of JSON data writer with better efficiency since the write tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
    NullWriter
    Null writer used to skip data, thus it doesn't actually write anything!
    TextDataParser
    New implementation of text data parser with better efficiency since the parsing tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
    TextDataWriter
    New implementation of text data writer with better efficiency since the write tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
    XmlDataWriter
    New implementation of XML data writer with better efficiency since the write tree is pre-computed during init instead of being re-evaluated while iterating through the component tree.
